6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Inflection and Mistral share a solid foundation of core features including File Upload, Api Access, Multilingual. Where Inflection pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Memory, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Mistral uniquely offers Web Search and Code Execution, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Inflection holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Mistral scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Inflection and Mistral offer flexible pricing models. Mistral stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Inflection requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
